>[!question]
>某班有最多不超过30人（具体人数由键盘输入）参加期末考试，最多不超过6门（具体门数由键盘输入）。定义结构体类型描述学生信息，每个学生信息包括：学号、姓名、多门课的成绩、总成绩和平均成绩。用结构体数组作为函数参数，编程实现如下菜单驱动的学生成绩管理系统。
（1）      录入每个学生的学号、姓名和各科考试成绩。
（2）      计算每门课程的总分和平均分。
（3）      计算每个学生的总分和平均分。
（4）      按每个学生的总分由高到低排出名次表。
（5）      按学号由小到大排出成绩表。
（6）      按姓名的字典顺序排出成绩表。
（7）      按学号查询学生排名极其考试成绩。
（8）      按姓名查询学生排名极其考试成绩。
（9）      按优秀（90~100）、良好（80~90）、中等（70~80）、及格（60~70）、不及格（0~59）5个类别，对每门课程分别统计每个类别的人数以及所占的百分比。
>
（10）    输出每个学生的学号、姓名、各科考试成绩以及每门课程的总分和平均分。
要求程序运行后先显示如下菜单，并提示用户输入选项：
>1.     Input record
>2.     Caculate total and average score of every course
>3.     Caculate total and average score of every student
>4.     Sort in descending order by total score of every student
>5.     Sort in ascending order by number
>6.     Sort in dictionary order by name
>7.     Search by number
>8.     Search by name
>9.     Statistic analysis for every course
>10.   List record
>11.     Exit
>Please input your choice:

----------

```c
#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
#include <stdlib.h>

#define MAX_STUDENTS 30
#define MAX_COURSES 6

typedef struct {
    char id[20];
    char name[50];
    float scores[MAX_COURSES];
    float total;
    float avg;
} Student;

int stu_num = 0;
int course_num = 0;
Student students[MAX_STUDENTS];
float course_total[MAX_COURSES];
float course_avg[MAX_COURSES];

// 函数声明
void inputRecords();
void calculateCourse();
void calculateStudent();
void sortByTotal();
void sortById();
void sortByName();
void searchById();
void searchByName();
void statisticAnalysis();
void listRecords();
void displayMenu();
void swapStudents(Student *a, Student *b);

int main() {
    int choice;
    
    while (1) {
        displayMenu();
        printf("Please input your choice: ");
        scanf("%d", &choice);
        
        switch (choice) {
            case 1: inputRecords(); break;
            case 2: calculateCourse(); break;
            case 3: calculateStudent(); break;
            case 4: sortByTotal(); break;
            case 5: sortById(); break;
            case 6: sortByName(); break;
            case 7: searchById(); break;
            case 8: searchByName(); break;
            case 9: statisticAnalysis(); break;
            case 10: listRecords(); break;
            case 0: 
                printf("Exit system.\n");
                exit(0);
            default:
                printf("Invalid choice! Please try again.\n");
        }
    }
    return 0;
}

void displayMenu() {
    printf("\n===== Student Grade Management System =====\n");
    printf("1. Input record\n");
    printf("2. Calculate total and average score of every course\n");
    printf("3. Calculate total and average score of every student\n");
    printf("4. Sort in descending order by total score of every student\n");
    printf("5. Sort in ascending order by number\n");
    printf("6. Sort in dictionary order by name\n");
    printf("7. Search by number\n");
    printf("8. Search by name\n");
    printf("9. Statistic analysis for every course\n");
    printf("10. List record\n");
    printf("0. Exit\n");
}

void inputRecords() {
    int i, j;
    
    printf("Enter number of students (1-%d): ", MAX_STUDENTS);
    scanf("%d", &stu_num);
    if (stu_num <= 0 || stu_num > MAX_STUDENTS) {
        printf("Invalid number of students!\n");
        stu_num = 0;
        return;
    }
    
    printf("Enter number of courses (1-%d): ", MAX_COURSES);
    scanf("%d", &course_num);
    if (course_num <= 0 || course_num > MAX_COURSES) {
        printf("Invalid number of courses!\n");
        course_num = 0;
        return;
    }
    
    for (i = 0; i < stu_num; i++) {
        printf("\nStudent %d:\n", i + 1);
        printf("ID: ");
        scanf("%s", students[i].id);
        printf("Name: ");
        scanf("%s", students[i].name);
        
        for (j = 0; j < course_num; j++) {
            printf("Score for course %d: ", j + 1);
            scanf("%f", &students[i].scores[j]);
            while (students[i].scores[j] < 0 || students[i].scores[j] > 100) {
                printf("Invalid score! Enter again (0-100): ");
                scanf("%f", &students[i].scores[j]);
            }
        }
    }
    printf("\n%d student records entered successfully!\n", stu_num);
}

void calculateCourse() {
    int i, j;
    
    if (stu_num == 0 || course_num == 0) {
        printf("No data available! Please input records first.\n");
        return;
    }
    
    for (j = 0; j < course_num; j++) {
        course_total[j] = 0;
        for (i = 0; i < stu_num; i++) {
            course_total[j] += students[i].scores[j];
        }
        course_avg[j] = course_total[j] / stu_num;
    }
    
    printf("\nCourse statistics:\n");
    for (j = 0; j < course_num; j++) {
        printf("Course %d - Total: %.2f, Average: %.2f\n", 
               j + 1, course_total[j], course_avg[j]);
    }
}

void calculateStudent() {
    int i, j;
    
    if (stu_num == 0 || course_num == 0) {
        printf("No data available! Please input records first.\n");
        return;
    }
    
    for (i = 0; i < stu_num; i++) {
        students[i].total = 0;
        for (j = 0; j < course_num; j++) {
            students[i].total += students[i].scores[j];
        }
        students[i].avg = students[i].total / course_num;
    }
    
    printf("\nStudent statistics calculated successfully!\n");
}

void swapStudents(Student *a, Student *b) {
    Student temp = *a;
    *a = *b;
    *b = temp;
}

void sortByTotal() {
    int i, j, rank;
    
    if (stu_num == 0) {
        printf("No data available! Please input records first.\n");
        return;
    }
    calculateStudent(); // 确保总分已计算
    
    // 冒泡排序（降序）
    for (i = 0; i < stu_num - 1; i++) {
        for (j = 0; j < stu_num - 1 - i; j++) {
            if (students[j].total < students[j + 1].total) {
                swapStudents(&students[j], &students[j + 1]);
            }
        }
    }
    
    printf("\nRanking by total score (descending):\n");
    printf("%-10s %-15s %-20s %-8s %-8s\n", "Rank", "ID", "Name", "Total", "Average");
    rank = 1;
    for (i = 0; i < stu_num; i++) {
        if (i > 0 && students[i].total < students[i-1].total) {
            rank = i + 1;
        }
        printf("%-10d %-15s %-20s %-8.2f %-8.2f\n", 
               rank, students[i].id, students[i].name, 
               students[i].total, students[i].avg);
    }
}

void sortById() {
    int i, j;
    
    if (stu_num == 0) {
        printf("No data available! Please input records first.\n");
        return;
    }
    
    // 冒泡排序（升序）
    for (i = 0; i < stu_num - 1; i++) {
        for (j = 0; j < stu_num - 1 - i; j++) {
            if (strcmp(students[j].id, students[j + 1].id) > 0) {
                swapStudents(&students[j], &students[j + 1]);
            }
        }
    }
    
    printf("\nSorted by student ID (ascending):\n");
    printf("%-15s %-20s %-8s %-8s\n", "ID", "Name", "Total", "Average");
    for (i = 0; i < stu_num; i++) {
        printf("%-15s %-20s %-8.2f %-8.2f\n", 
               students[i].id, students[i].name, 
               students[i].total, students[i].avg);
    }
}

void sortByName() {
    int i, j;
    
    if (stu_num == 0) {
        printf("No data available! Please input records first.\n");
        return;
    }
    
    // 冒泡排序（字典序）
    for (i = 0; i < stu_num - 1; i++) {
        for (j = 0; j < stu_num - 1 - i; j++) {
            if (strcmp(students[j].name, students[j + 1].name) > 0) {
                swapStudents(&students[j], &students[j + 1]);
            }
        }
    }
    
    printf("\nSorted by name (dictionary order):\n");
    printf("%-20s %-15s %-8s %-8s\n", "Name", "ID", "Total", "Average");
    for (i = 0; i < stu_num; i++) {
        printf("%-20s %-15s %-8.2f %-8.2f\n", 
               students[i].name, students[i].id, 
               students[i].total, students[i].avg);
    }
}

void searchById() {
    int i, j, found = 0;
    char targetId[20];
    
    if (stu_num == 0) {
        printf("No data available! Please input records first.\n");
        return;
    }
    
    printf("Enter student ID to search: ");
    scanf("%s", targetId);
    
    for (i = 0; i < stu_num; i++) {
        if (strcmp(students[i].id, targetId) == 0) {
            printf("\nStudent found:\n");
            printf("ID: %s\nName: %s\n", students[i].id, students[i].name);
            printf("Scores: ");
            for (j = 0; j < course_num; j++) {
                printf("%.2f ", students[i].scores[j]);
            }
            printf("\nTotal: %.2f, Average: %.2f\n", 
                   students[i].total, students[i].avg);
            found = 1;
            break;
        }
    }
    
    if (!found) {
        printf("Student with ID %s not found!\n", targetId);
    }
}

void searchByName() {
    int i, found = 0;
    char targetName[50];
    
    if (stu_num == 0) {
        printf("No data available! Please input records first.\n");
        return;
    }
    
    printf("Enter student name to search: ");
    scanf("%s", targetName);
    
    printf("\nSearch results:\n");
    for (i = 0; i < stu_num; i++) {
        if (strstr(students[i].name, targetName) != NULL) {
            printf("ID: %s, Name: %s, Total: %.2f, Average: %.2f\n", 
                   students[i].id, students[i].name, 
                   students[i].total, students[i].avg);
            found = 1;
        }
    }
    
    if (!found) {
        printf("No student named '%s' found!\n", targetName);
    }
}

void statisticAnalysis() {
    int i, j, k;
    const char *categories[5] = {
        "Excellent (90-100)",
        "Good (80-89)",
        "Medium (70-79)",
        "Pass (60-69)",
        "Fail (0-59)"
    };
    
    if (stu_num == 0 || course_num == 0) {
        printf("No data available! Please input records first.\n");
        return;
    }
    
    for (j = 0; j < course_num; j++) {
        int counts[5] = {0};
        
        for (i = 0; i < stu_num; i++) {
            float score = students[i].scores[j];
            if (score >= 90) counts[0]++;
            else if (score >= 80) counts[1]++;
            else if (score >= 70) counts[2]++;
            else if (score >= 60) counts[3]++;
            else counts[4]++;
        }
        
        printf("\n--- Course %d Statistics ---\n", j + 1);
        for (k = 0; k < 5; k++) {
            float percentage = (float)counts[k] / stu_num * 100;
            printf("%-20s:%4d (%5.1f%%)\n", 
                   categories[k], counts[k], percentage);
        }
    }
}

void listRecords() {
    int i, j;
    
    if (stu_num == 0 || course_num == 0) {
        printf("No data available! Please input records first.\n");
        return;
    }
    
    calculateCourse();
    calculateStudent();
    
    // 打印表头
    printf("\n%-10s %-15s %-20s", "No.", "ID", "Name");
    for (j = 0; j < course_num; j++) {
        printf(" Course%-2d", j + 1);
    }
    printf(" %-10s %-10s\n", "Total", "Average");
    
    // 打印学生数据
    for (i = 0; i < stu_num; i++) {
        printf("%-10d %-15s %-20s", i + 1, students[i].id, students[i].name);
        for (j = 0; j < course_num; j++) {
            printf("%8.2f", students[i].scores[j]);
        }
        printf("%10.2f%10.2f\n", students[i].total, students[i].avg);
    }
    
    // 打印课程总分
    printf("\n%-10s %-15s %-20s", "", "", "Course Total:");
    for (j = 0; j < course_num; j++) {
        printf("%8.2f", course_total[j]);
    }
    printf("\n");
    
    // 打印课程平均分
    printf("%-10s %-15s %-20s", "", "", "Course Average:");
    for (j = 0; j < course_num; j++) {
        printf("%8.2f", course_avg[j]);
    }
    printf("\n");
}
```
